Invocation Name: winter wonderland
des:
Welcome to the Winter Wonderland skill.

You can get Christmas cracker style jokes from Santa, Christmas Music from Santa, Facts about Christmas you probably did not know and great Christmas stories told by Santa.

Just ask Alexa to open Winter Wonderland and then ask for a joke, a fact, music or a Christmas story.

There are 9 Christmas Stories in this skill.

Enjoy
